/span>湯頭。<br />\n<br />\n豚骨風味<br />\n同牛丸無牛一樣道理"},{"pid":"3f19413a6b9c11e11282f8f06fa29ef39195967c","tid":1187492,"uid":46587,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T17:41:48.000Z","msg":"逼班中東佬食豬咪得囉<br />\n平時係新疆做慣做熟啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4cc80e046db853e20968aec11f6c7134ac4b0d9d","tid":1187492,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T17:43:02.000Z","msg":"偷偷加豬骨煲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5eb50bd6ef3f92aca02e8fad21614c079f1581bf","tid":1187492,"uid":47355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4192bd480be2fe44d4dde2ef2581b7660dd174e9","tid":1187492,"uid":4942,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"5df6835d6092bd62b781bbaa8927f67b60b7e6c0","tid":1187492,"uid":107186,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"735e63ba8853109655500dba09a9ea9bc825e353","tid":1187492,"uid":47355,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T16:53:18.000Z","msg":"班中東佬點會飲豬骨湯&hellip;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T17:09:05.000Z","msg":"內文咪有講囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T17:36:58.000Z","msg":"不吃豬肉的伊斯蘭教徒眾多的國家地區，為考量其需求而提供的拉麵，將會是融合雞肉等各式食材烹煮的<span style=\"color: red;\">豚骨風味</span>湯頭。<br />\n<br />\n豚骨風味<br />\n同牛丸無牛一樣道理"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T01:21:16.000Z","msg":"蟹柳冇蟹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1537ff294c5b75595895cb652835af345fcd9b6","tid":1187492,"uid":193131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T01:29:04.000Z","msg":"平時班清真撚唔係麻煩到，連個煲煮過豬肉都唔接受咩<br />\n駛唔駛換哂所有廚具呀"}]}